author: Doreen Christensen
title: Coupons: $3 off fresh food at Target
text:
Save $3 on fresh food with a Target coupon that may be accepted at Publix, too. 
The coupon is good on $15 purchases of fresh fruit and vegetables, bakery and deli items. 
Find the coupon by typing in "$3 off fresh food" in the search bar at the link below. Then print it and hit the back button on your browser to print a second one. 
Click here for the $3 coupon, which expires in November. 
"Like" Doreen's Deals page on Facebook ; follow Doreen Christensen on Twitter@PrettyGoodIdeas and sign up for Deals text alerts 
Two Trader Joe's stores are soon opening in South Florida. The chain, which stocks more than 3,000 private-label brands, drops anchor in Davie on Friday, Oct. 9, at 2296 S. University Drive. The second location opens at 1560 N. Federal Highway in Fort Lauderdale on Oct. 15. (Doreen Christensen)
